value.0: This man is short, with short dark brown hair and narrow blue eyes. He wears sturdy clothing and a work belt carrying a array of tools.
This man is short, with short dark brown hair and narrow blue eyes. He wears sturdy clothing and a work belt carrying a array of tools.
A flicker of fire suddenly sparks up from the floor, and within a moment, a spirit of the very flame itself forms. It burns dangerously, seeking the destruction of whatever stands in it's path.
A enraged ice elemental swinging blindly at you, cracks in the ice show continue exposure to torture and harm. It appears as a large chunk of jagged warped ice.
Burrowing below the surface of the ice, this massive worm seems intent on making you its next meal.
A large short human, with thick fingers fumbling with bottles.
Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.

This chain and amulet are masterfully crafted together to create a perfect loop of arcane energy. The material used give off and reflect no light. When the intended user places the chain around his or her neck, they immediately feel more resilient.
This terribly old, worn down Ring of Valkur seems unassuming to the normal eye, apart from the worn down and withered Silver and the cracked signet, from which small Salt Crystals seem to sprout...
A final gift from his beloved Captain.

A perfectly crafted two finger ring that fights tightly over the wearers index and middle fingers. Although it is made of high grade precious metal, its shine is dull and the ring itself seems to not reflect any light. Across the top the word <c >HOLD</c> is inscribed with great precision.

Ring 2 : Fast - A perfectly crafted two finger ring that fights tightly over the wearers index and middle fingers. Although it is made of high grade precious metal, its shine is dull and the ring itself seems to not reflect any light. Across the top the word <c >FAST</c> is inscribed with great precision.
